name: Vintage style necklace floral cameo with brass flower
description:
A stunning vintage style long chain necklace made with a pale blue floral cameo set in a gold tone bezel and handwired to a bronze chain and blue glass crackle beads and a brass filigree flower charm.

Materials - gold tone wire, foral cameo, bezel, brass flower, bronze chain, glass crackle beads.

Colours - Blue, navy, gold, brass, bronze

Size - The chain measures approximately 30 inches in length and has no clasp as can be put over the head.

Shipping - This necklace will come presented in a gift box with a bow and sent in a buble wrap envelope keeping it extra safe inside.

Thank you for looking xxx
